You are moving a column or aggregate and all of its associated headings
to a new location.  Move the cursor to the new position for the component
and then use the "Place" or "Shift" menu commands to select the new location.
The other associated components will be moved proportionally.

The menu commands are:

        MENU COMMANDS   SYNOPSIS
        -------------   --------
        Place           Place the selected component at the current position,
                        moving all associated components proportionally.

        Left            Move the component to the left border of the report,
                        moving all associated components proportionally.

        Center          Center the component, and move all associated
                        components proportionally.

        Right           Move the component to the right border of the report,
                        moving all associated components proportionally.

        Shift           Place the component at the current position,
                        shifting all components which are to the right.
                        Move all associated components proportionally.

        Help            Access the Ingres Help facility.

        End             Return to the Report Layout frame, without changing
                        the location of the component.
